* cd to your ppa directory
* ppa required conf
	- in your conf/config.inc.php: $conf['default_lang'] = 'english';

* setting your test environment
	- set your values in your selenium/tests/config.inc.php

/* deprecated
 * * setting the database & objects for test
 *	- edit selenium/tests/data/config.sql according to your config.tests.php
 *	- install test database & users :
 *		psql [...your options...]  -f selenium/tests/data/ppatests_install.sql
 */

* Running tests
	- point your browser on http://your_server/your_ppa_rep/selenium/TestRunner.html
	- on the left frame, "test suite" input, replace "../tests/TestSuite.html" with "tests/TestSuite.html", then click on "Go".
	- on the right frame, just click on "Run all tests" or "Run the selected test"

* cleaning your test database & objects
	- psql [...your options...] -f selenium/tests/data/ppatests_remove.sql
enjoy.
